  "texts": [
    "Another line of work seeks to generate text with the appearance of emotional content (e.g.",
    "Liu et al., 2021; Song et al., 2019; Wei et al., 2019).",
    "Recent work has harnessed persona-based prompting to reveal the varied stereotypes they can produce.",
    "Several of these have focused on using personas to elicit toxic content (Deshpande et al., 2023; Sheng et al., 2021; Wan et al., 2023b).",
    "Meanwhile, Cheng et al. (2023) investigated identitybased stereotypes in the persona descriptions generated by LLMs."
